Method Name: MiscUtil.getFileNameWithoutExtension
Method Code:
    public static String getFileNameWithoutExtension(File file) {
        String fileName = file.getName();
        int pos = fileName.lastIndexOf(".");
        if (pos > 0) {
            fileName = fileName.substring(0, pos);
        }
        return fileName;
    }

